sequenceDiagram
    participant HW as 输入设备(触屏/按键)
    participant IMS as InputManagerService
    participant ID as InputDispatcher(Native)
    participant WS as 目标窗口(App)
    participant AMS as AMS

    HW->>IMS: 硬件中断 → 输入事件
    IMS->>ID: notifyMotion() / notifyKey()
    ID->>ID: dispatchOnce()
    ID->>ID: findFocusedWindowTargetLocked()

    alt 窗口就绪
        ID->>WS: 通过 InputChannel 派发事件
        WS->>WS: dispatchTouchEvent() 处理
        WS->>ID: finishInputEvent() 反馈已消费
        Note over ID: 重置等待计时
    else 窗口忙(上一事件未处理完)
        ID->>ID: 记录 waitStartTime
        loop 每次 dispatchOnce 循环检查
            ID->>ID: currentTime - waitStartTime > 5s ?
        end
        ID->>ID: onAnrLocked() 超时!
        ID->>AMS: InputManagerService 回调
        AMS->>AMS: inputDispatchingTimedOut()
        AMS->>AMS: AnrHelper.appNotResponding()
    end
